(63531, 80330, 0, 1, '痞子的故事', '每個人走到一個階段有時候會以為什麼事都可以得心易手,但錯了!!人越驕傲就失敗的越快.......真的要好好去思考我們有的一切是從哪來的!!', '2013-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 1, 'I do like what I want   \nBut you can`t made judge of me\nI thought I had a crush on you\nBut then you are not my type             \n 	   \nYou know that what I`m who I`m \nAlways do everything\nI try my best to change\nBut how can I do like this\n\nSomeone hate you but somebody loves u \nSometh made you feel so cool\nI can write a new song for you\nSo God pleace tell me how to do \n\nI want to live my life with a reason\nHow can I overcome this situation\nDon`t be waste your time it`s won`t come back\nAnd I know I don`t have to worry  \n', '', 221, '', 'Danny', 'Danny', '根號時差', '根號時差', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-05-12 23:45:45', '2015-03-12 14:00:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
